OL,3,CThe 'Great Fire' that changed
OL,4,CNewcastle and Gateshead forever
OL,6,FKatie Cole has been discovering the
OL,7,Fimpact of the little known Great Fire
OL,8,Fof Newcastle and Gateshead 170 years on
OL,10,FAn explosion 170 years ago this week
OL,11,Fsparked a fire that would forever
OL,12,Fchange the face of Newcastle and
OL,13,FGateshead.
OL,15,FMany on Tyneside believed the end of
OL,16,Fthe world was upon them in the early
OL,17,Fhours of 6 October 1854 as a fire took
OL,18,Fhold of Gateshead.
