OL,3,CThe 'Great Fire' that changed
OL,4,CNewcastle and Gateshead forever
OL,6,FIt soon spread across the Tyne -
OL,7,Fclaiming the lives of 53 people and
OL,8,Finjuring more than 500.
OL,10,FThe Great Fire of Newcastle and
OL,11,FGateshead has faded into relative
OL,12,Fobscurity - sparking an effort on
OL,13,FTyneside to make sure it is not
OL,14,Fforgotten.
OL,16,FTom Elwick, from the Discovery Museum,
OL,17,Fin Newcastle, said: "All of the big
OL,18,Fevents like the Great Fire of London
OL,19,Fget all the glory but this local event
OL,20,Fis something that changed the
OL,21,FQuayside."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/9
