OL,3,CThe 'Great Fire' that changed
OL,4,CNewcastle and Gateshead forever
OL,6,FThe fire started at woollen yarn
OL,7,Ffactory, Wilson's Worsted, which was
OL,8,Fnext to a timber yard and warehouse
OL,9,Fcontaining explosive chemicals.
OL,11,FIt was a fatal combination.
OL,13,FPolice Constable John Ewart, of the
OL,14,FNewcastle Constabulary, spotted the
OL,15,Ffire and raced across the Old Tyne
OL,16,FBridge to warn the local fire brigade.
OL,18,FFlames quickly spread to surrounding
OL,19,Fbuildings and a lumber yard.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/9
