OL,3,CThe 'Great Fire' that changed
OL,4,CNewcastle and Gateshead forever
OL,6,FStanding next to Wilson's factory was
OL,7,Fthe warehouse of Bertram and Spencer
OL,8,Fwhich contained a perfect cocktail of
OL,9,Fchemicals.
OL,11,F"The chemicals inside would glow when
OL,12,Fburnt, giving off a bluey purple
OL,13,Fglow," Tom explained. "The sulphur in
OL,14,Fthere became almost like lava which
OL,15,Fcame spewing out of windows."
OL,17,FIt was a terrifying spectacle for
OL,18,Fthose watching on.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/9
