OL,3,CThe 'Great Fire' that changed
OL,4,CNewcastle and Gateshead forever
OL,6,FTom continued: "A lot of the buildings
OL,7,Fwere from Tudor times - made from wood
OL,8,Fand were very close together so fire
OL,9,Fspread quickly through those
OL,10,Fbuildings."
OL,12,FIt was the perfect recipe for a town-
OL,13,Fwide inferno which spread across the
OL,14,Friver to Newcastle's Quayside.
OL,16,FCrowds gathered on the Old Tyne
OL,17,FBridge, where the Swing Bridge now
OL,18,Fstands, to seek safety.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/9
