OL,3,CThe 'Great Fire' that changed
OL,4,CNewcastle and Gateshead forever
OL,6,FThey watched as the stereo inferno
OL,7,Fengulfed both sides of the river,
OL,8,Flooking on as sulphur poured like lava
OL,9,Fout of Bertram and Spencer's warehouse
OL,10,Fwindows.
OL,12,FFirefighters arriving atop horse-drawn
OL,13,Ffire engines took one-and-a-half days
OL,14,Fto bring the blaze under control.
OL,16,FFire engines arrived from all over the
OL,17,Fregion with many from Hexham, Durham,
OL,18,FMorpeth and Berwick brought to
OL,19,FNewcastle by rail.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/9
