OL,3,CThe 'Great Fire' that changed
OL,4,CNewcastle and Gateshead forever
OL,6,FDespite the crowds watching then,
OL,7,Fknowledge of the this major event has
OL,8,Ffizzled.
OL,10,FTom now runs events for schools where
OL,11,Fthey are hosting a 'Great Fire' week
OL,12,Fto educate children on the event.
OL,14,FHe said "People come into the museum
OL,15,Fand you say 'oh, do you know about the
OL,16,FGreat Fire of Newcastle and
OL,17,FGateshead?'.
OL,19,F"Lots of them say 'no i didn't have a
OL,20,Fclue, I didn't know this took place'.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/9
