OL,3,CThe 'Great Fire' that changed
OL,4,CNewcastle and Gateshead forever
OL,6,F"Local schools know this story quite
OL,7,Fwell - it's quite a popular topic
OL,8,Fwithin local history.J"The Quayside
OL,9,Fwould not be what it is today without
OL,10,Fthis event."
OL,12,FAlongside the destruction of the
OL,13,FQuayside, 53 people died and more than
OL,14,F500 were injured in the fire - more
OL,15,Fthan were officially recorded to have
OL,16,Fperished in the Great Fire of London.
OL,18,FDamage to property came in at around
OL,19,F#500,000, the equivalent of more than
OL,20,F#42.5m in today's money.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/9
