OL,3,CThe 'Great Fire' that changed
OL,4,CNewcastle and Gateshead forever
OL,6,FOnly a few buildings on the Newcastle
OL,7,FQuayside survived that day.
OL,9,FBessie Surtees House, on Sandhill, in
OL,10,FNewcastle, is one such building which
OL,11,Fstill stands, just as it has since it
OL,12,Fwas built as a merchant's house in the
OL,13,F16th century.
